  "text": "Human trials with oligofructose and inulin include those with a controlled diet and crossover feeding trials, although the dose, substrate, duration, and volunteers vary ( Table 2 ). The efficacy of inulin has also been evaluated with a view to its administration to formula-fed infants [CITATION_1] .",
